MagniCube
=========
A 4x4x4 LED cube driven by a NXP MagniV MCU

Directories:
============
|
+-Hardware              - Everything needed to build a MagniCube RevA
|
+-Software              - Source files (ASM and Forth) of the calculators
|                          firmware
|
+-Tools                 - Tools written for the development of the MagniCube
|
+-Subprojects           - Repository clones of the projects that MagniCube
                          is based on

